{"tid":1408514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一手]觀塘發現疑似中共記者","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:06:22.000Z","uid":183141,"like":191,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7f82d832f6c190bd5e5207ac1352be0cac3b79","tid":1408514,"uid":183141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"(借朋友ac上黎講少少野)<br />\n<br />\n我想講講頭先行過 <br />\n見到香港人應該係諗住搬貨落車<br />\n然後就有個男人拎住cam去影車牌<br />\n咁我就行過去<br />\n我:👧🏻 中共記者:🙎🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n👧🏻：唔好意思 想問下你咩台？<br />\n🙎🏻&zwj;♂️：港台呀 做咩？<br />\n👧🏻 : 哦～無事無事<br />\n然後行埋左一邊 發現唔對路<br />\n叫佢出示翻港台記者證<br />\n佢就兇我🤬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6a0BWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6a0BWy.png&h=15e6d050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6ceGof.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6ceGof.png&h=a74c6039&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24Txs3h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24Txs3h.png&h=d70b1021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後有議員同在場男人幫手先發現佢係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">南天記者</span><br />\n<br />\n(有片但無人識po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"6b6b9f6c2ad14dbd28afbc688b8a15a42a206734","tid":1408514,"uid":224095,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"樓主好勁<br />\n連登神探"},{"pid":"e15b37acbd30ce25c420e727ead1cec02e9e1da6","tid":1408514,"uid":143827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80c46679b3be85ffa02339bdfef5d1b47cbba4e7","tid":1408514,"uid":146520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"打傷咗上白車果個係咪佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d098193ac93514291ead12647e40ebc231cb42d0","tid":1408514,"uid":183141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80c46679b3be